quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  10,43,No muri bo hari abakwitegereza (ariko ntibabone ibyo Allah yaguhaye bijyanye n’urumuri rw’ukwemera). Ese wayobora abigira nk’abatabona kabone n’ubwo baba batabona koko
  10,44,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah nta muntu ajya ahemukira na rimwe, ahubwo abantu ni bo bihemukira ubwabo"
  10,45,"N’umunsi azabakoranyiriza hamwe, (bazamera) nk’aho batigeze babaho (ku isi) uretse isaha imwe yo ku manywa, kandi bazamenyana. Rwose babandi bahakanye kuzahura na Allah barahombye, kandi ntibayobotse"
  10,46,"Kandi (yewe Muhamadi) n’iyo twakwereka bimwe mu byo tubasezeranya (ukiri ku isi), cyangwa tukakuzuriza igihe cyawe (ugapfa), (uko byagenda kose) iwacu ni ho bazagarurwa. Hanyuma Allah akaba umuhamya w’ibyo bakoraga"
  10,47,"Na buri muryango (umat) wahawe intumwa; ubwoIntumwa yabo izaba ije (gutanga ubuhamya ku munsi w’imperuka), bazacirwa imanza mu butabera kandi ntibazarenganywa"
  10,48,"Baranavuga bati \"Iryo sezerano (imperuka) rizasohora ryari niba koko muri abanyakuri"
  10,49,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ku bwanjye, nta bushobozi mfite bwo kugira ikibi nakwikiza cyangwa ngo ngire icyiza nakwimarira uretse icyo Allahyashaka. Buri muryango (umat) wagenewe igihe ntarengwa (cyo kubaho); iyo igihe cyabo kigeze, ntibarindirizwa na gato cyangwa ngo bihutishwe mbere yacyo"
  10,50,"Vuga uti \"Nimumbwire! Ese ibihano bye (Allah) biramutse bibagezeho nijoro cyangwa ku manywa (mwabihungira he)? Nonese kuki inkozi z’ibibi zisaba ko byihutishwa (kandi ntaho zabihungira)"
  10,51,Ese biramutse bibagezeho ni bwo mwabyemera?(Icyo gihe muzabwirwa muti) ese ubu (ni bwo mwemeye) kandi mwarajyaga musaba ko byihutishwa
  10,52,"Hanyuma babandi bihemukiye babwirwe bati \"Ngaho nimwumve ububabare bwibihano bihoraho. Ese hari ikindi muhaniwe kitari ibyo mwakoraga"
  10,53,"Barakubaza bati \"Ese ibyo uvuga (byerekeranye n’imperuka) ni ukuri?\" Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Yego! Ndahiye ku izina rya Nyagasani wanjye! Ni ukuri! Kandi ntaho mwacikira(Allah)"